item.description: Getting There BBC, MediaCityUK, Salford, M50 2EQ Salford Quays is less than four miles from Manchester city centre, 12 miles from Manchester airport and a short distance from the M60. The SatNav postcode is M50 2BH. Bus, train and Metrolink information at https://www.tfgm.com. Please arrive from 9am onwards to be processed by security. Please bring photo id to speed your admittance. Parking If I travel by car where can I park and what is the cost?
